page_title: What's new in Azure OpenAI Service?
page_description: Learn about the latest news and features updates for Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: May 2023### Java & JavaScript SDK support- NEW Azure OpenAI preview SDKs offering support for JavaScript and Java.### Azure OpenAI Chat Completion General Availability (GA)- General availability support for:  - Chat Completion API version `2023-05-15`.  - GPT-35-Turbo models.  - GPT-4 model series.   If you are currently using the `2023-03-15-preview` API, we recommend migrating to the GA `2023-05-15` API. If you are currently using API version `2022-12-01` this API remains GA, but does not include the latest Chat Completion capabilities.> [!IMPORTANT]> Using the current versions of the GPT-35-Turbo models with the completion endpoint remains in preview.  ### France Central- Azure OpenAI is now available in the France Central region. Check the models page, for the latest information on model availability in each region.
